c=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 勁"},{"pid":"3b4d76c9d1bd359249aaeee7694351e99cad342b","tid":1121468,"uid":33939,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T10:39:45.000Z","msg":"嗱，我都認為係蘋果日報手法好有問題。但香港人係咁撚八掛無知架啦，點會去狙擊蘋果。"},{"pid":"a490635acc0725b00320674813fc4af593585bbc","tid":1121468,"uid":36702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T10:40:52.000Z","msg":"佢老公唔知有無搵「黃心穎」呢 ？"},{"pid":"9644dc4f6927901b3650a5b7ae9e3ff4c7def26b","tid":1121468,"uid":134071,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"7ef4eff3e006246a350d4ad044a4857c4ada2690","tid":1121468,"uid":171399,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"2c95c95c5fd872abea16d6835a3592da6500a036","tid":1121468,"uid":134071,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T10:36:01.000Z","msg":"屈穎妍會否狙擊以下傳媒?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/AOrzZzT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAOrzZzT.png&h=2e7b6d30&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/kcdKCmz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkcdKCmz.jpg&h=90561c5d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/QFp56eU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQFp56eU.jpg&h=6f4249dc&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T10:39:21.000Z","msg":"有哂圖 巴打你秒殺左佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 勁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T10:43:46.000Z","msg":"星島日報最新文章仲勁過偷拍, 話有&quot;一名不願透露姓名的鄰居&quot;報料就有文章出.  <br />\n<br />\n梁振英叫蘋果公開報料者身份, 會否叫埋星島公開報料者身份?<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.stheadline.com/inews-content.php?cat=f&amp;nid=81004\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.stheadline.com%2Finews-content.php%3Fcat%3Df%26nid%3D81004&d=%2FIqeUsS3N0qecbTP5cC9OE5YX6KrfwXAFWAh9WWXcag%3D&h=c02c65b5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.stheadline.com%2Finews-content.php%3Fcat%3Df%26nid%3D81004&h=6f1e98c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.stheadline.com/inews-content.php?cat=f&amp;nid=81004</a><br />\n<br />\n  不過，最驚人的是原來除了安仔和馬明外，鄰居經常看見不同的圈中人到訪香閨，一名不願透露姓名的鄰居跟本報記者爆料，見過黃心穎與一組合的男結他手，以及商台一名男主持十指緊扣返家，在電梯內舉止親暱，令人側目。當追問是哪個組合成員？鄰居說︰「成日劃眼綫嗰個呀，就嚟開演唱會個隊！」"},{"pid":"92b9415b207f07befb5eccfb002cb18233150fa4","tid":1121468,"uid":242301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T10:44:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bea23e74392037a265d8e55fd87ec9373f8718a2","tid":1121468,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"quote":{"pid":"92b9415b207f07befb5eccfb002cb18233150fa4","tid":1121468,"uid":242301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T10:44:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T10:48:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/6/61/06la2p6.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20140604184600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F6%2F61%2F06la2p6.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20140604184600&h=93b298a9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7a0c4695c05a2f8bf76df9a8944fb923bc1d270e","tid":1121468,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T10:49:54.000Z","msg":"搞咩?<br />\n連藍C都學班黃屍豬咁玩全城中伏 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d50dacd35e7d8271aa0eb5c8c6012833753bbb56","tid":1121468,"uid":17765,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T10:54:20.000Z","msg":"在六四天安門事件時，曾參與黃雀行動的屈穎妍等人於1995年8月18日以旅遊為名在福建沿海地區非法蒐集中國軍事機密，於8月20日被當地群眾發現並舉報。福建國家安全機關對他們進行了審查，查明<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">屈穎妍等人的行為觸犯了《中華人民共和國國家安全法》、《中華人民共和國軍事設施保護法》</span></strong></span>，嚴重危害了國家安全，並於8月25日根據《中華人民共和國國家安全法》第三十條規定，依法將該人等被公安拘捕後驅逐出境。[3]<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屈臭閪 你就快被引渡喇喎 <br />\n咁關心人哋偷食做乜？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"435b8a4